Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Disable WMPNetworkSvc (Windows Media Player Network Sharing Service)
; This service shares your music, videos, and media library over the local network using DLNA.
; It allows devices like Smart TVs, consoles (Xbox/PlayStation), or other PCs to access your media.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\WMPNetworkSvc]
"Start"=dword:00000004